OL,7,FA deep dive into the crisis engulfing
OL,8,Fadult social care has revealed almost
OL,9,Fa third of councils are no longer
OL,10,Fconfident they can even meet their
OL,11,Fbasic legal duties towards elderly and
OL,12,Fvulnerable residents next year.
OL,14,FResearch from the Local Government
OL,15,FAssociation, shared exclusively with
OL,16,FITV News, lays bare the scale of fear
OL,17,Ffelt by those leading this work in
