OL,7,FA survey with dozens of adult social
OL,8,Fcare leads suggests just 8% are very
OL,9,Fconfident about meeting their
OL,10,Fstatutory duties for 2025/26 - down
OL,11,Ffrom 27% when looking ahead towards
OL,12,Fthis year, 2024/25.
OL,14,FThat means many people in - are
OL,15,Ffailing to get it - with visits either
OL,16,Fbeing cancelled or shortened over many
OL,17,Fyears.
