OL,7,F'You want to spend more time with
OL,8,Fpeople, but you just can't': Julie
OL,9,FSansom told ITV News the lack of
OL,10,Fresources has made it 'stressful' to
OL,11,Fgive people even a basic level of care
OL,13,FThe fears about meeting the legal
OL,14,Frequirements come despite eight out of
OL,15,F10 councils forecasting having to cut
OL,16,Fspending on other community services
OL,17,Fsuch as parks, libraries and leisure
OL,18,Fcentres to try to protect funding.
