OL,7,F"We are at a critical point, for
OL,8,Fpeople who draw on care, councils and
OL,9,Fthe sector," said Cllr David
OL,10,FFothergill - the LGA's social care
OL,11,Flead.
OL,13,FThe Conservative lead on Somerset
OL,14,FCouncil said the situation "simply
OL,15,Fisn't good enough" and argued adult
OL,16,Fsocial care needed urgent attention.
OL,18,F"This must be top of the in-tray for
OL,19,Fany incoming government."
